nglview¶

IPython/Jupyter . NGL Viewer . , RCSB PDB, simpletraj (MDTraj, PyTraj, MDAnalysis, ParmEd, RDKit, ASE, HTMD, biopython, cctbx, pyrosetta, schrodinger.structure).

Ссылки:¶

  • https://github.com/nglviewer/nglview
  • http://nglviewer.org/ngl/gallery/index.html
  • http://nglviewer.org/nglview/release/v0.6.2.3/index.html#
  • https://europepmc.org/article/PMC/6031024

Установка¶

Python 3.

  • conda:
    conda install nglview -c conda-forge ( jupyter-nbextension enable nglview --py --sys-prefix)
  • pip:
    pip install nglview
    jupyter-nbextension enable nglview --py --sys-prefix
  • nglview:
    conda upgrade nglview --force

nglview Jupyter Lab : jupyter labextension install nglview-js-widgets (https://github.com/arose/nglview/blob/master/devtools/nglview-jupyterlab.sh)

Подробнее об установке написано здесь:¶

  • https://github.com/nglviewer/nglview

, .
show_file(path) , NGL (pdb, gro, mol2, sdf, dx, ..), (path)
show_pdbid(pdbid) PDBID, RCSB PDB
show_simpletraj(struc_path, traj_path) , simpletraj
show_mdtraj(traj) MDTraj (mdtraj.Trajectory: http://mdtraj.org/development/api/generated/mdtraj.Trajectory.html)
show_pytraj(traj) PyTraj (pytraj.Trajectory: https://amber-md.github.io/pytraj/latest/_api/pytraj.trajectory.html)
show_parmed(structure) ParmEd (parmed.structure.Structure: https://parmed.github.io/ParmEd/html/api/parmed/parmed.structure.html?highlight=structure)
show_mdanalysis(univ) MDAnalysis Universe AtomGroup univ (https://docs.mdanalysis.org/1.0.0/documentation_pages/core/universe.html, https://userguide.mdanalysis.org/1.0.0/atomgroup.html)
show_rdkit(mol) RDKit (rdkit.Chem.rdchem.Mol: (https://www.rdkit.org/docs/source/rdkit.Chem.rdchem.html)
show_ase(atoms) ASE (ASE Atoms: https://wiki.fysik.dtu.dk/ase/ase/atoms.html)
show_asetraj(traj) ASE (ASE Trajectory: https://wiki.fysik.dtu.dk/ase/ase/io/trajectory.html#:~:text=The%20ase.,that%20is%20not%20a%20requirement.)
show_pymatgen(struct) pymatgen Structure (https://pymatgen.org/usage.html#structures-and-molecules)
show_htmd(mol) HTMD Molecules (https://software.acellera.com/docs/latest/htmd/tutorials/htmd-molecules.html)
show_biopython(mol) Biopython (Biopython structural entities: https://biopython.org/docs/1.75/api/Bio.PDB.Entity.html#Bio.PDB.Entity.Entity)
show_iotbx(mol) cctbx's iotbx structure (CCTBX: https://cctbx.github.io/)
show_rosetta(pose) PyRosetta's Pose (pyrosetta.rosetta.core.pose: https://graylab.jhu.edu/PyRosetta.documentation/pyrosetta.rosetta.core.pose.html)
show_iodata(obj) iodata's IOData (IOData: https://github.com/theochem/iodata)
show_psi4(obj) psi4 (psi4.core.Molecule: http://www.psicode.org/psi4manual/master/api/psi4.core.Molecule.html)
show_qcelementary QCelementary Molecule ()
show_openbabel openbabel (OBMol: http://openbabel.org/dev-api/classOpenBabel_1_1OBMol.shtml)
show_prody prody's Ensemble AtomGroup (http://prody.csb.pitt.edu/manual/reference/ensemble/ensemble.html, http://prody.csb.pitt.edu/manual/reference/atomic/atomgroup.html)
